      <div class="outright-payment box">
        <div class="img" style="background-image: url(/images/icons8-card-payment-96\ \(1\).png); height: 75px;"></div>
        <h4>Outright Payment</h4>
        <p>You like the price you’ve seen with Print House UK and you want to proceed – that’s great news. We are able to take secure payments at our facility on 20 Service Road, Potters Bar EN6 1QA or you can bank transfer to us (we’ll provide the details). <br> <br>
