      </div>

      <div class="lease-plan box">
        <div class="img" style="background-image: url(/images/icons8-lease-96.png);"></div>
        <h4>Lease Plans</h4>
        <p>Cashflow is a consideration for every business. So, if you’d like to pay a fixed amount to rent the machine without a hefty sum up front, we can provide this facility through our financing partners. <br> <br>

          With a rental agreement, after a fixed period, you may not own the machine, but that allows you to upgrade at the end of the contract,  What’s good for you, is good for us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="textbox-container">
      <div class="payment-plan box">
        <div class="img" style="background-image: url(/images/icons8-plan-96.png); width: 50px;"></div>
        <h4>Payment Plans</h4>
        <p>Alternatively, we can provide the exact machine(s) with the specification you require on a tailored payment plan that meets your budget and costs associated with the hardware & technology you are seeking to secure. This way you can spread the costs and repayment requirements ensuring you can operate, grow and prosper whilst paying amounts that are agreeable with you. <br> <br>
          We’re here to make life as easy as possible and therefore will balance the proposed repayments that meet your satisfaction. You can invest more as a deposit, reducing the monthly payments or vice versa – let’s talk through the options.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="print-plan box">
        <div class="img" style="background-image: url(/images/icons8-print-96.png);width: 55px;" ></div>
        <h4>Print Plans</h4>
        <p>
          No two customers have the same requirements; therefore, each payment plan is designed around each and every customer. This is one of the areas that elevates us above the competition. With print plans, we can undertake a thorough analysis of your print requirements, speculate on what you’ll use in the short, medium, and long-term and then propose a print plan is delivered to meet your needs.<br> <br>
          We appreciate there are many options which our customers can benefit from.  By speaking to our experienced team, you can make a balanced decision therefore securing the hardware and expertise you need at a cost that makes perfect sense.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

